           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4571-3608"))
Description: RNAseq and microarray data analysis tools for oncological gene expression analysis. This package provides functions for differential expression analysis, gene set enrichment analysis, and visualization of gene expression data.
